    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宇宙中最黑暗的星球上，你孤身一人。<br>你唯一的伙伴，是一台 8 位计算机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >靠着它的 8 位界面维持生存，<br>你必须挑战这颗星球无法居住的黑暗地表，深入充满敌意的地底世界。<br>研究陌生的外星植物，收集神秘的科学数据——但请保持警惕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/ab16b84ecd63100e17ad988584cb1439.poster.avif?t=1769704904\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/ab16b84ecd63100e17ad988584cb1439.webm?t=1769704904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/ab16b84ecd63100e17ad988584cb1439.mp4?t=1769704904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，随着你逐步深入，这颗星球的物理法则开始扭曲。<br>时间破碎，记忆混乱，连你自身的存在也开始模糊。<br>在令人窒息的黑暗中生存下来——但请记住：<br>最大的威胁，可能并不来自四周的虚空……<br>而是来自你逐渐崩溃的内心深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在体验经典的 2D 游戏机制时，<br>你将逐渐发现其中蕴含的规律，与现实世界也有所共鸣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/4c1386349a7ab732790b7950ea93b7fd.webp?t=1769704904\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/4c1386349a7ab732790b7950ea93b7fd.poster.avif?t=1769704904\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=282 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/d09a3539c0d24cde9fb93894d724058f.poster.avif?t=1769704904\" width=300 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/d09a3539c0d24cde9fb93894d724058f.webm?t=1769704904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/d09a3539c0d24cde9fb93894d724058f.mp4?t=1769704904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于这台计算机的图像与通讯能力受限，<br>你必须解读由像素组成的 2D 画面，<br>并将它们转化为实时的解决方案，以克服一个个难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的宇宙飞船，如今已成为一个小型基地，<br>是这颗星球上唯一的安全地带。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在这里休息、储存物品、接收新的任务。<br>但有些地方不对劲。你本应是孤身一人——<br>可为什么，总感觉有人，或者某种东西，在暗中注视着你？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338860/extras/6fe8379944cff82bc4f2d2e5b7cb9d4f.avif?t=1769704904\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你听见空荡走廊中的脚步声，<br>看到不属于你的影子掠过墙壁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许，你并不是一个人。<br>又或者，你从来就不是一个人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第三人称生存恐怖体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式视觉叙事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的武器与装备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >针对低配置电脑与掌上设备优化</p></li></ul>",
